## Design Overview

Lusano's website embodies an elegant, minimalist design system that prioritizes typography and warm, earthy tones. The design is characterized by a sophisticated brown color palette ranging from deep chocolate to warm beige, creating a luxurious, heirloom-quality aesthetic. The typography system uses EB Garamond, a classic serif font, throughout the site, emphasizing elegance and timelessness. The layout is clean and spacious, with generous white space allowing content and product imagery to breathe. The design system emphasizes subtle animations, smooth transitions, and a sophisticated user experience that reflects the brand's commitment to quality craftsmanship.

